title: YouTube paid version launched 6 things to know
text:
YouTube paid version launched: 6 things to know 
Times Of India Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
1. 
YouTube will co-exist with the paid version The launch of YouTube Red does not mean the end of YouTube as we know it. The free version of YouTube will still be available as a free, ad-supported product....
